`combineLatest` takes N input observables and emits a combined value every time any of them emits — but only once every single source has produced its first value. That gating matters for forms: if a field hasn't emitted yet you do not want to render a half-populated ViewModel. Seeding each source with an initial value via `BehaviorSubject` or `startWith` lets the combined stream emit immediately.

